  <brief_title>The Effect of Preoperative Anxiety Level on the Induction Dose of Propofol and Minimum Alveolar Concentration (MAC) Hour of Sevoflurane During Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Preoperative Anxiety Level on the Induction Dose of Propofol and MAC-hour of Sevoflurane During Thyroidectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
