  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the level of anxiety, and to check the correlation of induction
      dose and the amount of sevoflurane to keep anesthetic depth in in female patients undergoing
      thyroidectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
